ontent-asset\">\n          By subscribing to MCM Global AG newsletter, I consent that my email address may be used to send me regular communication about MCM collection, news and offers as described in our <a class=\"mod_link\" href=\"\/pages\/legal-terms#PRIVACY-POLICY\" title=\"Legal Terms\">privacy policy<\/a>. You are entitled to withdraw your consent at any time.*\n        <\/div>\n      <\/label>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- Submit Button -->\n    <div class=\"form-row-button mcm-mb-half-x mcm-popup-submit\">\n      <button type=\"submit\" class=\"mcm-button-primary-default mcm-full-width subscribe-btn\">Subscribe<\/button>\n    <\/div>\n  {% endform %}\n  <div class=\"content-asset\">Offer redeemable once per customer on first order only. Exclusions apply. Not valid on sale merchandise. Cannot be combined with any other offer. <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\ninput.news-input.input-text {\n    margin-top: 5%;\n    width:50%\n}\n\/* Custom Checkbox Styles *\/\ninput[type=\"checkbox\"] {\n    -webkit-appearance: checkbox; \/* Re-enable checkbox appearance for WebKit browsers *\/\n    appearance: checkbox; \/* Standard property for other browsers *\/\n    width: 20px; \/* Width of the checkbox *\/\n    height: 20px; \/* Height of the checkbox *\/\n    cursor: pointer; \/* Changes cursor to pointer to indicate clickable area *\/\n}\n.content-asset {\n    font-family: 'MCM Favorit Variable';\n    width: 80%;\n}\n\/* Custom Check Mark using pseudo-element *\/\ninput[type=\"checkbox\"]:checked::before {\n    content: '✔'; \/* Unicode check mark *\/\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 4px;\n    color: white;\n    font-size: 16px;\n}\n.mcm-privacy.required input[type=\"checkbox\"] {\n    -webkit-appearance: checkbox !important;\n    appearance: checkbox !important;\n    width: 20px;\n    height: 20px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    display: inline-flex;\n    border: 1px solid #000;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: visible;\n}\n\n.checkbox-m .content-asset {\